article_id:419,category_name:News,title_name:Announcing a Platinum Showcase!,image_path:,message:<div>A Platinum Showcase will go live <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1556604000"></span>.</div><div><br></div><div>The Platinum Showcase is a limited summon showcase that works similar to a tenfold summon, in that one summon will get you 10 results. The difference between a regular tenfold summon and this Platinum Showcase is that a 5★ dragon is guaranteed to appear.</div><div><br></div><div>During the period, players are limited to doing the 5★ dragon guaranteed Platinum Showcase summon only once, and these summons can only be performed with diamantium (purchase required).</div><div><br></div><div>Note: The pool for this showcase includes limited-time 5★ adventurers Marth, Fjorm, and Veronica, but they are not guaranteed summons for this showcase.</div><div><br></div><div>Availability period for the Platinum Showcase:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1556604000"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1557813540"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Get a closer look at some of the 5★ dragons, one of which is guaranteed to appear in the tenfold summon.</div><div><br></div><div>5★ dragons eligible for guaranteed appearance as the 10th summon:</div><div><div class="summonPickUp">
