						<li>The fire-wielding gatekeeper of the underworld.<br>A free spirit, she often shirks her work in favor of<br>play. The sentient, puppet-like dogs on her hands<br>are called Coco and Mimi, and their intelligence<br>allows them to speak and attack on their own.</li>
