			<div class="status">
				<div class="title">Dragon Details</div>
				<div class="param">
					<ul>
						<li>A motherly dragon living a quiet life in the forest.<br>She has been warming the same egg for many<br>hundreds of years, eagerly awaiting the first<br>signs of hatching. To threaten her egg is to<br>incur both a dragon's and a mother's wrath.</li>
