	<dl><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/756879fc2f94c1df98ecd39bf3dd90ae2.png"></span><span>(Water) HP +40%</span></dt><dd><div>If the user is attuned to Water: <br>increases HP by 40%.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/561f0cc02896bcc3c7580180041730282.png"></span><span>(Water) Overdrive Punisher +60%</span></dt><dd><div>If the user is attuned to Water: <br>increases damage to enemies in overdrive state<br>by 60%.</div></dd></dl></div></div></div><div><br></div><div>The stats shown here represent each dragon at maximum level, maximum bond, and fully unbound. They do not represent the stats when first obtained.</div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. For more information about summoning, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Showcase Info and check the Details tab.</div><div>2. For appearance rates and other information, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Showcase Info and check the More Info tab, or select Appearance Rates and check the Appearance Rates section.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1556244000,update_time1556241075